<HH> ============= Screen: ABC reference diagram ================ </HH>

<IntakeGate ready="!@fba2_completion_checkbox.value">
<Markdown> </Markdown>
<Markdown id="fba2_abc_reference">
## ABC Reference: Escape Example

| **Antecedent** (Before) | → | **Behavior** | → | **Consequence** (After) |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Teacher gives a difficult task | → | Student puts head down | → | Task is removed or delayed |

**Function: Escape** — The student's behavior (putting head down) is maintained by negative reinforcement (removal of the aversive task).

---

