<HH> ============= Screen: Johnny's function ==================== </HH>

<Vertical id="fba2_johnny_function">
<MarkupProblem id="fba2_johnny_function_choice" title="Function of Johnny's Behavior"><![CDATA[
## What is the function of Johnny's behavior?

>>Now that you've identified the ABCs of Johnny's bedtime behavior, what is the function of his running out of the room?<<

( ) Access to preferred activity/object
( ) Attention
(x) Escape
( ) Sensory

[explanation]
The function is **escape**. Johnny's running away is maintained by negative reinforcement — he successfully avoids or delays going to bed (the aversive event). The antecedent (being told to go to bed) triggers the behavior (running away), and the consequence (not having to go to bed right away) reinforces it.
[/explanation]
]]></MarkupProblem>
</Vertical>


